@startuml
title Activity: Crime Investigation Workflow

start
:Case Assignment;
:Initial Scene Assessment;
fork
  :Collect Physical Evidence;
fork again
  :Interview Witnesses;
fork again
  :Review Surveillance;
end fork
:Analyze Collected Data;
:Identify Suspect(s);
if (Enough Evidence?) then (Yes)
  :Obtain Arrest Warrant;
  :Execute Arrest;
else (No)
  :Continue Investigation;
  :Gather Additional Evidence;
endif
:Prepare Case File;
:Submit to Prosecutor;
stop
@enduml
